response.overview: Forensic psychologist and detective Alex Cross travels to North Carolina and teams with escaped kidnap victim Kate McTiernan to hunt down "Casanova," a serial killer who abducts strong-willed women and forces them to submit to his demands. The trail leads to Los Angeles, where the duo discovers that the psychopath may not be working alone.
response.tagline: Smart girls. Pretty girls. Missing girls.
response.title: Kiss the Girls

titles.title: … denn zum Küssen sind sie da
